tal team. The design of tissue boxes often incorporates features that promote convenience and ease of use, such as pop-up dispensers or decorative packaging that complements the aesthetic of the dental office. Some tissue boxes are equipped with antimicrobial coatings or additives to inhibit the growth of bacteria and maintain a hygienic environment. Dental practices routinely restock tissue boxes to ensure that patients always have access to clean tissues throughout their visit. Overall, tissue boxes are essential accessories in dental offices, contributing to patient comfort, hygiene, and infection control while enhancing the overall experience of dental care. ', '2024-05-24 03:03:33', '9981c20bef3fb1337ce53f64f0298e7b', 1, 1, 1, '*', '2024-05-04 05:33:06', NULL, '2024-05-04 05:33:06', NULL, 0, 0, 3, );
